This directory contains the JavaScript source modules for the chess UI.
These modules are merged by build-chess.py / build-chess.sh into chess.html.

License classification by file:
  - game-logic.js: GPL v3 (derived from DroidFish)
      PGN disambiguation and SAN notation logic from DroidFish.
      Copyright (C) Peter Österlund. Modifications Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.
  - ai-bridge.js: GPL v3 (derived from DroidFish)
      Engine communication patterns from DroidFish.
      Copyright (C) Peter Österlund. Modifications Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.
  - ui.js: GPL v3 (derived from DroidFish)
      UI layout and interaction patterns from DroidFish.
      Copyright (C) Peter Österlund. Modifications Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.
  - tablebase.js: GPL v3 (derived from DroidFish)
      PGN parsing logic (GameTree/PgnToken/PgnScanner) from DroidFish.
      Copyright (C) Peter Österlund. Modifications Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.
  - eco-data.js: AGPL v3 (original)
      ECO opening data from lichess-org/chess-openings (CC0).
      Code is original — not derived from DroidFish.
  - index.html.tpl: AGPL v3 (original CSS/HTML template)
  - build-chess.sh: AGPL v3 (original build script)

The combined output (chess.html) is a combined work. The GPL v3 JavaScript
modules and AGPL v3 template retain their respective licenses. Since AGPL v3
imposes stricter requirements, its obligations effectively cover the entire
combined output.

See the root-level LICENSE-AGPL v3, LICENSE-GPL v3, and NOTICE files
for full license texts and attribution details.
